WEBVTT

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:04.318
When you successfully identify a strategic account where co-selling could

00:00:04.318 --> 00:00:08.636
provide a definitive, deal-winning edge, absolute speed and flawless procedural

00:00:08.636 --> 00:00:12.953
execution are highly critical. You must immediately open an internal

00:00:12.953 --> 00:00:17.271
ad-hoc request to accurately signal the opportunity, proactively align with

00:00:17.271 --> 00:00:21.589
your designated Partner Development Manager to establish early momentum, and

00:00:21.589 --> 00:00:25.907
extensively utilize the comprehensive playbooks heavily documented on our internal

00:00:25.907 --> 00:00:30.225
hub. Common Reasoning Trap: Waiting until the late stages of

00:00:30.225 --> 00:00:34.543
a sales cycle to engage AWS is a critical error.

00:00:34.543 --> 00:00:38.860
The AWS Account Manager requires time to navigate their own

00:00:38.860 --> 00:00:43.178
internal structures and influence the customer's procurement team. Late engagement

00:00:43.178 --> 00:00:47.496
nullifies their ability to act as a strategic bridge.
